			<span>商业</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">硅谷总迷恋长寿和改变世界，这次爱上了一台复杂的榨汁机</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-03 07:57:04 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">3</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">26</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/24874.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
